{"tid":364987,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"每日三杯茶記凍飲，一個月肥4磅","createTime":"2017-08-19T00:21:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-20T17:18:26.000Z","uid":29314,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ba0afeea8edae85ec59329135da031d4be2a69bf","tid":364987,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T00:21:37.000Z","msg":"營養師吳耀芬（Kathy）&hellip;&hellip;指若一日三餐均飲喝這類飲品，如早餐喝一杯咖啡，中午喝一杯檸檬茶，晚上喝一杯奶茶的話，&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;如果維持一個月這樣的飲食習慣，一個月有機會增重3至4磅。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n凍檸茶（124kcal）和<br />\n凍檸水（124kcal），<br />\n飲一杯已經相等於吃了約半碗白飯，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n凍奶茶（146.2kcal）和<br />\n凍咖啡（159.3kcal），<br />\n相等於約大半碗飯的熱量，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n凍好立克（202kcal）與<br />\n凍朱古力（181kcal），<br />\n每杯相等於約一碗白飯的熱量，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由於凍檸茶和凍檸水不含奶，故不含脂肪，其餘四杯的脂肪含量相等於半茶匙至一茶匙的油。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而六杯飲品的糖份相若，<br />\n糖份亦高達4至5茶匙。"},{"pid":"4ff87ee161b0f6a83c5a1984faa37bac871e2d1f","tid":364987,"uid":22644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T00:24:33.000Z","msg":"飲開走甜 少甜點計"},{"pid":"029d4567fa58a487f393ef3acccdd8529d8755c2","tid":364987,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T00:25:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飲開走甜 少甜點計</blockquote><br />\n其實少甜係咪真係少左糖？"},{"pid":"a006fc885daed5595b285a2aaece43b98ca53b1c","tid":364987,"uid":81234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T00:27:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>飲開走甜 少甜點計</blockquote><br />\n其實少甜係咪真係少左糖？</blockquote><br />\n飲得出"},{"pid":"7a9f8848063a61ca5c7966de557c4a9f8eb5b890","tid":364987,"uid":4285,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T00:29:08.000Z","msg":"咁真係好飲嘛"},{"pid":"c7973ae48f0cf3bff4a0d94c874b20da62f2c105","tid":364987,"uid":59451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T00:31:07.000Z","msg":"飲開走甜 唔會有咩卡路里掛"},{"pid":"7773d5f9b793617b50bf29e763a71be6b357b