03b1f37c3efe47c3412a65b82071a48943e6507d","tid":364987,"uid":51233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T01:31:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>飲開走甜 少甜點計</blockquote><br />\n其實少甜係咪真係少左糖？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好難講，要睇佢個杯原本有幾多糖，杯茶有幾濃<br />\n同埋凍飲飲落冇咁甜，杯少甜隨時多過兩包糖"},{"pid":"7ebd0e08fa0b4bc333ab10fa152156aad837fc1d","tid":364987,"uid":22507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T01:33:20.000Z","msg":"有糖尿病先啦"},{"pid":"fe857359c249c577403ded37beac56a13a710249","tid":364987,"uid":84373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T01:34:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>飲開走甜 少甜點計</blockquote><br />\n其實少甜係咪真係少左糖？</blockquote><br />\n唔係,其實係少左鹽</blockquote><br />\n一般就沖定2底<br />\n一種有糖 一種無糖<br />\n平時直接比晒有糖<br />\n半糖咪55溝<br />\n走甜就直接比無糖<br />\n<br />\n不過一般叫咩少甜走甜人數比較少<br />\n所以無糖果底都放得幾耐下</blockquote><br />\nPS：果陣紅茶洛糖嘅比例<br />\n以容量黎計 一杯會有5~中6分1嘅容量 係糖<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ccb8d2e5efe4103eff84407e95b4dfbabb7ee1","tid":364987,"uid":8157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T01:37:32.000Z","msg":"唔做運動先成日計住計住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2380fcc812058b49c74a209bff17573f99d5f44","tid":364987,"uid":65128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T01:38:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fd2b09fc66cfa2ffa875b1219c5de668068ce1e3","tid":364987,"uid":16528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T01:40:31.000Z","msg":"又係啲垃圾營養師出埋啲垃圾文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一個人肥真係咁撚簡單咩"},{"pid":"a6e9b1f21070277449ab2764fc1f1718e0eb4714","tid":364987,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T01:44:49.0